highlights.text: “Higa” by Arthur Nery has been on Top Songs Philippines the longest, at 1870 days straight.
December Avenue has the most spots on Top Songs Philippines. “Saksi Ang Langit” is the highest at #2.
“See You Again (feat. Kali Uchis)” by Tyler, The Creator and Kali Uchis is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Philippines, up 42 spots at #126.
